This is a placeholder file for the default book image.
In a real deployment, you would replace this with an actual image file.
You can download a book placeholder image from sites like:
- https://picsum.photos/seed/book/200/300.jpg
- https://via.placeholder.com/200x300/cccccc/666666?text=Book

For now, the system will use CSS fallbacks and error handling to display
appropriate placeholders when images are missing.
